&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F97583;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&#x2F;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #79B8FF;&quot;&gt;html&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F97583;&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now we know for certain how files are loaded - &lt;code&gt;include(base64_decode($page) . &#x27;.php&#x27;)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;. We need to find a way to load &lt;code&gt;&#x2F;flag.txt&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; even though &lt;code&gt;.php&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; is always appended.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
